Uses of Package
popt4jlib.PS

  • Packages that use popt4jlib.PS 
    Package Description
    popt4jlib.PS
    Particle Swarm Optimization Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
  • Classes in popt4jlib.PS used by popt4jlib.PS 
    Class and Description
    ChromosomeSelectorIntf
    class specifies the topology operator for selecting a particle among the list of all particles in an island (sub-population).
    ChromosomeVelocityAdderIntf
    class specifies the operator for adding velocity objects to chromosome objects, with the help of some parameters specified in a HashMap.
    DPSO
    A parallel implementation of the Particle Swarm Optimization algorithm for function optimization, implementing also the SubjectIntf and ObserverIntf objects by extending the GLockingObservableObserverBase class, so that it may be combined with other optimization processes and produce better results.
    DPSOIndividual
    auxiliary class not part of the public API
    DPSOThread
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    DPSOThreadAux
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    NewVelocityMakerIntf
    specifies how to create new velocity objects.
    RandomVelocityMakerIntf
    specifies how to create random velocity objects, given some parameters included in a HashMap object.
